Subject: Alfred Hitchcock Presents…Signatures In Suspense (1999)
Object: Bernard Herrmann (tracks: 5 to 9, 11 to 13, 16, 18), Dimitri Tiomkin (tracks: 2, 3)

Subject: Alfred Hitchcock Presents…Signatures In Suspense (1999)
Object: It’s a soundtrack compilation from many of Hitchcock best known movies.

Subject: Alfred Hitchcock Presents…Signatures In Suspense (1999)
Object: The collaboration with Herrmann was central in his cinematography and it’s important to underline the role of music in the movie production, especially Hitchcock’s suspenseful one.
